section.fonts-container
  .title fonts

  ul.font-list
    li.active Default
    li Cursive
    li Monospace

section.emoji-container
  .title emoji

  .emoji-toggle-container
    .status disabled
    = input#emoji-toggle.toggle type='checkbox' checked=emojiActive
    label for='emoji-toggle'

  img.lazy data-original="<%= image_path('emoji-dropdown.gif') %>"

  p Just type a colon (:) to trigger the emoji dropdown. The selected emoji will appear in the resulting maptile.
